  <nav class="article-toc" aria-label="Table of contents">
    <h2>On this page</h2>
    <ol>
      <li><a href="#what-is-bill">What is an itemized medical bill?</a></li>
      <li><a href="#bill-vs-eob">Bill vs. EOB</a></li>
      <li><a href="#key-sections">Key sections on your bill</a></li>
      <li><a href="#cpt-codes">CPT and revenue codes</a></li>
      <li><a href="#facility-professional">Facility vs. professional fees</a></li>
      <li><a href="#chargemaster">Chargemaster and list prices</a></li>
      <li><a href="#common-lines">Common line items explained</a></li>
      <li><a href="#insurance-on-bill">How insurance appears on your bill</a></li>
